author: Jack Power
title: Coronavirus: Republic reports 31 further deaths as cases pass 10,000
description: Officials record 527 new confirmed cases while HSE insists testing backlog will be cleared
content:
Thirty-one more people have died from the coronavirus in the Republic, as the number of known cases has now surpassed 10,000.
